{"thag16.10:0.1":"Theragatha 16.10 ","thag16.10:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.10:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.10:0.4":"Parapariyattheragatha ","thag16.10:1.1":"Samanassa ahu cinta, ","thag16.10:1.2":"pupphitamhi mahavane; ","thag16.10:1.3":"Ekaggassa nisinnassa, ","thag16.10:1.4":"pavivittassa jhayino. ","thag16.10:2.1":"“Annatha lokanathamhi, ","thag16.10:2.2":"titthante purisuttame; ","thag16.10:2.3":"Iriyam asi bhikkhunam, ","thag16.10:2.4":"annatha dani dissati. ","thag16.10:3.1":"Sitavataparittanam, ","thag16.10:3.2":"hirikopinachadanam; ","thag16.10:3.3":"Mattatthiyam abhunjimsu, ","thag16.10:3.4":"santuttha itaritare. ","thag16.10:4.1":"Panitam yadi va lukham, ","thag16.10:4.2":"appam va yadi va bahum; ","thag16.10:4.3":"Yapanattham abhunjimsu, ","thag16.10:4.4":"agiddha nadhimucchita. ","thag16.10:5.1":"Jivitanam parikkhare, ","thag16.10:5.2":"bhesajje atha paccaye; ","thag16.10:5.3":"Na balham ussuka asum, ","thag16.10:5.4":"yatha te asavakkhaye. ","thag16.10:6.1":"Aranne rukkhamulesu, ","thag16.10:6.2":"kandarasu guhasu ca; ","thag16.10:6.3":"Vivekamanubruhanta, ","thag16.10:6.4":"vihamsu tapparayana. ","thag16.10:7.1":"Nica nivittha subhara, ","thag16.10:7.2":"mudu atthaddhamanasa; ","thag16.10:7.3":"Abyaseka amukhara, ","thag16.10:7.4":"atthacinta vasanuga. ","thag16.10:8.1":"Tato pasadikam asi, ","thag16.10:8.2":"gatam bhuttam nisevitam; ","thag16.10:8.3":"Siniddha teladharava, ","thag16.10:8.4":"ahosi iriyapatho. ","thag16.10:9.1":"Sabbasavaparikkhina, ","thag16.10:9.2":"mahajhayi mahahita; ","thag16.10:9.3":"Nibbuta dani te thera, ","thag16.10:9.4":"paritta dani tadisa. ","thag16.10:10.1":"Kusalananca dhammanam, ","thag16.10:10.2":"pannaya ca parikkhaya; ","thag16.10:10.3":"Sabbakaravarupetam, ","thag16.10:10.4":"lujjate jinasasanam. ","thag16.10:11.1":"Papakananca dhammanam, ","thag16.10:11.2":"kilesananca yo utu; ","thag16.10:11.3":"Upatthita vivekaya, ","thag16.10:11.4":"ye ca saddhammasesaka. ","thag16.10:12.1":"Te kilesa pavaddhanta, ","thag16.10:12.2":"avisanti bahum janam; ","thag16.10:12.3":"Kilanti manne balehi, ","thag16.10:12.4":"ummattehiva rakkhasa. ","thag16.10:13.1":"Kilesehabhibhuta te, ","thag16.10:13.2":"tena tena vidhavita; ","thag16.10:13.3":"Nara kilesavatthusu, ","thag16.10:13.4":"sasangameva ghosite. ","thag16.10:14.1":"Pariccajitva saddhammam, ","thag16.10:14.2":"annamannehi bhandare; ","thag16.10:14.3":"Ditthigatani anventa, ","thag16.10:14.4":"idam seyyoti mannare. ","thag16.10:15.1":"Dhananca puttam bhariyanca, ","thag16.10:15.2":"chaddayitvana niggata; ","thag16.10:15.3":"Katacchubhikkhahetupi, ","thag16.10:15.4":"akicchani nisevare. ","thag16.10:16.1":"Udaravadehakam bhutva, ","thag16.10:16.2":"sayantuttanaseyyaka; ","thag16.10:16.3":"Katham vattenti patibuddha, ","thag16.10:16.4":"ya katha satthugarahita. ","thag16.10:17.1":"Sabbakarukasippani, ","thag16.10:17.2":"cittim katvana sikkhare; ","thag16.10:17.3":"Avupasanta ajjhattam, ","thag16.10:17.4":"samannatthotiacchati. ","thag16.10:18.1":"Mattikam telacunnanca, ","thag16.10:18.2":"udakasanabhojanam; ","thag16.10:18.3":"Gihinam upanamenti, ","thag16.10:18.4":"akankhanta bahuttaram. ","thag16.10:19.1":"Dantaponam kapitthanca, ","thag16.10:19.2":"puppham khadaniyani ca; ","thag16.10:19.3":"Pindapate ca sampanne, ","thag16.10:19.4":"ambe amalakani ca. ","thag16.10:20.1":"Bhesajjesu yatha vejja, ","thag16.10:20.2":"kiccakicce yatha gihi; ","thag16.10:20.3":"Ganikava vibhusayam, ","thag16.10:20.4":"issare khattiya yatha. ","thag16.10:21.1":"Nekatika vancanika, ","thag16.10:21.2":"kutasakkhi apatuka; ","thag16.10:21.3":"Bahuhi parikappehi, ","thag16.10:21.4":"amisam paribhunjare. ","thag16.10:22.1":"Lesakappe pariyaye, ","thag16.10:22.2":"parikappenudhavita; ","thag16.10:22.3":"Jivikattha upayena, ","thag16.10:22.4":"sankaddhanti bahum dhanam. ","thag16.10:23.1":"Upatthapenti parisam, ","thag16.10:23.2":"kammato no ca dhammato; ","thag16.10:23.3":"Dhammam paresam desenti, ","thag16.10:23.4":"labhato no ca atthato. ","thag16.10:24.1":"Sanghalabhassa bhandanti, ","thag16.10:24.2":"sanghato paribahira; ","thag16.10:24.3":"Paralabhopajivanta, ","thag16.10:24.4":"ahirika na lajjare. ","thag16.10:25.1":"Nanuyutta tatha eke, ","thag16.10:25.2":"munda sanghatiparuta; ","thag16.10:25.3":"Sambhavanamyevicchanti, ","thag16.10:25.4":"labhasakkaramucchita. ","thag16.10:26.1":"Evam nanappayatamhi, ","thag16.10:26.2":"na dani sukaram tatha; ","thag16.10:26.3":"Aphusitam va phusitum, ","thag16.10:26.4":"phusitam vanurakkhitum. ","thag16.10:27.1":"Yatha kantakatthanamhi, ","thag16.10:27.2":"careyya anupahano; ","thag16.10:27.3":"Satim upatthapetvana, ","thag16.10:27.4":"evam game muni care. ","thag16.10:28.1":"Saritva pubbake yogi, ","thag16.10:28.2":"tesam vattamanussaram; ","thag16.10:28.3":"Kincapi pacchimo kalo, ","thag16.10:28.4":"phuseyya amatam padam. ","thag16.10:29.1":"Idam vatva salavane, ","thag16.10:29.2":"samano bhavitindriyo; ","thag16.10:29.3":"Brahmano parinibbayi, ","thag16.10:29.4":"isi khinapunabbhavo”ti. ","thag16.10:29.5":"… Parapariyo thero … ","thag16.10:29.6":"Visatinipato nitthito. ","thag16.10:30.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag16.10:30.1":"Adhimutto parapariyo, ","thag16.10:30.2":"telakani ratthapalo; ","thag16.10:30.3":"Malukyaselo bhaddiyo, ","thag16.10:30.4":"anguli dibbacakkhuko; ","thag16.10:30.5":"Parapariyo dasete, ","thag16.10:30.6":"visamhi parikittita; ","thag16.10:30.7":"Gathayo dve sata honti, ","thag16.10:30.8":"pancatalisa uttarinti. "}